<title>CHINA: Trading in Hopewell shares suspended.</title>
<headline>Trading in Hopewell shares suspended.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1997-07-15</dateline>
<text>
<p>Trading in shares of Hopewell Holdings Ltd was suspended on Tuesday at the company's request pending an announcement, the Hong Kong stock exchange said.</p>
